WEBVTT

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:32.456
However, neuromodulation
does not mean neuro-repair.

00:01:33.301 --> 00:01:35.608
And the dream of functional neurosurgeons

00:01:35.632 --> 00:01:37.270
is to repair the brain.

00:01:39.222 --> 00:01:40.619
I think

00:01:40.643 --> 00:01:42.478
that we are approaching this dream.

00:01:42.502 --> 00:01:44.135
And I would like to show you

00:01:45.161 --> 00:01:47.096
that we are very close to this.

00:01:48.022 --> 00:01:51.133
And that with a little bit of help,

00:01:51.157 --> 00:01:54.524
the brain is able to help itself.

00:01:56.516 --> 00:01:58.685
So the story started 15 years ago.

00:01:59.156 --> 00:02:01.176
At that time, I was a chief resident